  "title": "Storeman cum Driver",
  "description": "<p>• Manage the store’s inventory of tools and equipment including Personal Protection Equipment (PPE), ensuring accurate record keeping and organization of the inventory.</p>\n<p>• Receive and process incoming inventory and goods, including unloading, verifying, and storing incoming items.</p>\n<p>• Pick and pack orders accurately and efficiently.</p>\n<p>• Prepare orders for delivery and load goods onto vehicles for transportation.</p>\n<p>• Deliver products to customers on time and ensure proper handling and delivery.</p>\n<p>• Verify delivery instructions and ensure that all paperwork and documentation are complete.</p>\n<p>• Drive company vehicles safely and follow all traffic regulations and guidelines.</p>\n<p>• Perform routine maintenance on Company vehicles, such as cleaning and refueling.</p>\n<p>• Assist in maintaining a clean and organized store and work area.</p>\n<p>• Communicate with management and other team members to ensure the efficient operation of the store and transportation activities.</p>\n<p>• Ensure compliance with company policies and procedures and adhere to health and safety regulations.</p>",
